[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.  

This hand would be one point too strong to <b>Open</b> 1NT, but it fits the 15-18 range to <b>Overcall</b> 1NT. Partner responds 2\C.  

Don't get your systems crossed. Partner did not make a cue-bid, he is using Stayman. Since you have no 4-card Major suit you answer 2\D. Partner now says 2NT and the ball is in your court. 

This is just a plain old 1NT/Stayman sequence. Partner is inviting, and since you have 18 points you accept.}

